# ATLAS Services Directory

This directory contains all ATLAS-related service classes for API communication.

Services to be implemented:
- deployment.service.ts - Deployment CRUD and lifecycle operations
- ai-analysis.service.ts - AI analysis, risk assessment, recommendations
- approval.service.ts - Approval workflows and authority validation
- exception.service.ts - Exception request management
- agent.service.ts - Agent execution and monitoring
- query-builder.service.ts - Dynamic query building and execution
- atlas-api-client.service.ts - Base API client with common functionality
- atlas-signalr.service.ts - Real-time SignalR communication
- atlas-config.service.ts - Configuration management
- atlas-error-handler.service.ts - Error handling and resilience patterns
